(On front of base:) &lt;br&gt;
THEODORE ROOSEVELT&lt;br&gt;
1858–1919&lt;br&gt; 
(On left side of base:)&lt;br&gt; 
GOVERNOR OF THE STATE OF NEW YORK&lt;br&gt;
